# a basic fm oscillator

@ in note
@ in modoffset
@ in fmdepth
@ in reset

@ out out


+ miditofreq mtof1
> _in_@note mtof1@in

+ add fmoff
> _in_@note fmoff@in1
> _in_@modoffset fmoff@in2

+ miditofreq mtof2
> fmoff@out mtof2@in

+ sinosc modosc
> mtof2@out modosc@freq
# uncomment to reset mod osc phase too
# > _in_@reset modosc@reset

+ sinosc carrier
> mtof1@out carrier@freq
> modosc@out carrier@fm
> _in_@fmdepth carrier@fmdepth
> _in_@reset carrier@reset

> carrier@out _out_@out

